Set Shell zsh

Output detail.gif

Set FontSize 13
Set Width 800
Set Height 400
Set Padding 15
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Theme "nord"
Require lpx

Hide

Type@10ms lpx earth.gif
Enter
Sleep 1s

Show

Sleep 500ms

Type "d"

Sleep 500ms

Space
Sleep 2s
Type "d"
Sleep 1s
Type "d"
Sleep 1s
Space

Sleep 500ms
